{"word":"προγράφω","slug":"προγράφω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προγράφω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρό\">πρό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:γράφω\">γράφω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘write in a time that is prior’, <b>write about before <a href='B:520 15:4'>Ro 15:4</a>; write previously <a href='B:560 3:3'>Eph 3:3</a>; announce before in writing <a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 4</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘set forth for general notice’, <b>depict, portray;</b> or <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> more narrowly defined image, <b>to placard <a href='B:550 3:1'>Gal 3:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πρόγονος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πρόδηλος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}